{"tid":2388442,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google：我係主動移除Robinhood十萬個負評，又點？","createTime":"2021-01-31T06:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T08:27:47.000Z","uid":226155,"like":6,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"42d7dbb09125ca2c07ddb0af9a1200738f35e89f","tid":2388442,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"全美最受歡迎的網上證券公司羅賓俠公司（Robinhood）1月28日一度禁止用戶購買包括遊戲驛站公司（GameStop）及AMC在內的被網民散戶「炒起」的美股。對此不滿的用戶發起運動，到Google應用程式（App）商店Google Play對羅賓俠App給予一星評價。Google其後向美國媒體The Verge證實公司正主動移除負面評價。<br />\n<br />\n【GameStop／WSB／AMC／Robinhood／挾淡倉】不少用戶在Google Play對羅賓俠App給予1星評價（滿分為5星），導致它的評價由27日的約4星，急跌至28日的1星。不過Google採取行動後，羅賓俠App整體評價升回接近4星。<br />\n<br />\n美國科技網站Gizmodo在28日報道，Google刪除最少10萬個負面評價。<br />\n<br />\nThe Verge在28日報道，Google政策明確禁止有意操縱程式評分的評論。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，Google表示，公司曾特別對它認為違反有關政策的評分採取行動。"},{"pid":"895d556b7c2ab98596a6da0664e0e4a0b9d60b58","tid":2388442,"uid":226155,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"睇住一間公司由dont be evil 黃金時代墜落到依家咁"},{"pid":"ecbb0d7d7c518f30d1684b529cd7de85f6f31306","tid":2388442,"uid":74361,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:48:12.000Z","msg":"我課金好多比左拜登，驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967dd1f47834af5b09a15696ac1245a07ddd8b34","tid":2388442,"uid":249094,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"左膠big tech 沆瀣一氣，唔鍾意就del comment del account <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次google做得好呀，左膠終於求仁得仁"},{"pid":"531981bb40960725d5e5462e8e33df3ecd3df235","tid":2388442,"uid":2419,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫有意操縱 痴撚線<br />\n個app服務令人失望都唔俾得一星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81af651f6e2dfc77058482fc84e00e7cae30e0e6","tid":2388442,"uid":12628,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17